{"version":4,"code":"66261d80","title":"The Lighthouse Code","description":"Twelve-year-old Tom Rinaldi is dreading a boring summer in the sleepy coastal village of Santa Marea—until a mysterious flickering light in the old lighthouse leads him and his cousin Irene into a decades-old mystery involving a vanished uncle, coded messages, hidden wartime documents, and a secret worth protecting. As they decode clues left behind by Zeno Rinaldi, they discover that the true treasure isn’t gold, but the truth—and it’s far more dangerous.","show_table_of_contents":true,"apply_automatic_indentation":true,"last_update_date":1752421695400,"last_cloud_sync_date":1752304204740,"last_backup_date":1752421713303,"cover":"","revisions":[{"number":1,"date":1752240196259,"book_progresses":[{"year":2025,"month":7,"day":11,"word_count":2946}],"categories":[{"code":"9c3bcad6","title":"Themes","color":4288423856,"ranking":1,"metadata_groups":[{"code":"cf0e2684.jpg","title":"General","ranking":1,"metadata_elements":[{"code":"ac9df54d.jpg","title":"Importance","ranking":1,"is_relevant":true},{"code":"969ed489.jpg","title":"Symbol","ranking":2,"is_relevant":true}]}],"items":[{"code":"ef69e892","title":"Truth as Treasure","synopsis":"Truth and knowledge are more valuable - and more dangerous - than material treasure.","ranking":1,"status":"ad3819b2","item_metadatas":[{"metadata_element":"ac9df54d.jpg","value":"Core"},{"metadata_element":"969ed489.jpg","value":"The restored lighthouse"}]},{"code":"6acabda8","title":"Family and Legacy","synopsis":"The bond of a family across generations helps solve a long-standing mystery and restore a lost name.","ranking":2,"status":"ad3819b2","item_metadatas":[{"metadata_element":"ac9df54d.jpg","value":"High"},{"metadata_element":"969ed489.jpg","value":"Zeno's journal, the final letter."}]},{"code":"2c0fce79","title":"Curiosity and Courage","synopsis":"Tom's transformation from reluctant visitor to brave truth-seeker underscores the vale of courage fueled by curiosity.","ranking":3,"status":"ad3819b2","item_metadatas":[{"metadata_element":"ac9df54d.jpg","value":"Supporting"},{"metadata_element":"969ed489.jpg","value":"The brass key"}]}]},{"code":"a5329840","title":"Events","color":4280391411,"ranking":2,"items":[{"code":"49e8add7","title":"The Light in the Lighthouse","synopsis":"Tom sees a strange flickering from the supposedly abandoned lighthouse, triggering the mystery.","ranking":1,"status":"ad3819b2"},{"code":"12aaee20","title":"Discovery of Zeno's journal","synopsis":"Tom and Irene find Zeno's journal, filled with clues, maps and coded entries.","ranking":2,"status":"ad3819b2"},{"code":"624e4be1","title":"The Boathouse Revelation","synopsis":"The children find Zeno's hidden cache of classified documents in an old boathouse.","ranking":3,"status":"ad3819b2"},{"code":"f9cf101c","title":"The Final Confrontation","synopsis":"Arturo reveals his identity and intention, and the children complete Zeno's mission.","ranking":4,"status":"ad3819b2"}]},{"code":"efb87ede","title":"Characters","color":4278228616,"ranking":3,"metadata_groups":[{"code":"94f91159.jpg","title":"Personal","ranking":1,"metadata_elements":[{"code":"5656e0b7.jpg","title":"Age","ranking":1,"is_relevant":true},{"code":"11256834.jpg","title":"Skills","ranking":2,"is_relevant":true}]},{"code":"ff53cd26.jpg","title":"Story","ranking":2,"metadata_elements":[{"code":"42bc76ed.jpg","title":"Role","ranking":1,"is_relevant":true},{"code":"7ab4b635.jpg","title":"Arc","ranking":2,"is_relevant":true},{"code":"1ea2a136.jpg","title":"Status","ranking":3,"is_relevant":true}]}],"tags":[{"code":"93f841a9","title":"Absent force","color":4288585374},{"code":"62647291","title":"Fallen","color":4294937189},{"code":"05aa7761","title":"Heroic","color":4286695300},{"code":"9ebd8391","title":"Mentor","color":4294953512}],"items":[{"code":"7ef69440","title":"Tommaso \"Tom\" Rinaldi","synopsis":"A curious 12-year-old who transforms from screen-obsessed to courageous adventurer.","ranking":1,"status":"ad3819b2","item_tags":[{"tag":"05aa7761"}],"item_names":[{"code":"2950d705","name":"Tommaso","ranking":1},{"code":"e90908a3","name":"Rinaldi","ranking":2},{"code":"85676f52","name":"Tom","ranking":3}],"item_metadatas":[{"metadata_element":"5656e0b7.jpg","value":"12"},{"metadata_element":"42bc76ed.jpg","value":"Protagonist"},{"metadata_element":"7ab4b635.jpg","value":"Growth (reluctant to brave)"}],"item_relationships":[{"other_item":"98a09da8","description":"Cousin to","ranking":1,"is_relevant":true},{"other_item":"d5d0771b","description":"Grandson of","ranking":2,"is_relevant":true},{"other_item":"ce38b4dc","description":"Grand-nephew of","ranking":3,"is_relevant":false}],"item_pictures":[{"picture":"","ranking":1}]},{"code":"98a09da8","title":"Irene Rinaldi","synopsis":"A clever and adventurous 14-year-old who leads much of the investigation.","ranking":2,"status":"ad3819b2","item_tags":[{"tag":"05aa7761"}],"item_names":[{"code":"d985eab4","name":"Irene","ranking":1}],"item_metadatas":[{"metadata_element":"5656e0b7.jpg","value":"14"},{"metadata_element":"11256834.jpg","value":"Navigation, codes"},{"metadata_element":"42bc76ed.jpg","value":"Co-protagonist"},{"metadata_element":"7ab4b635.jpg","value":"Steady leader"}],"item_relationships":[{"other_item":"7ef69440","description":"Cousin to","ranking":1,"is_relevant":true},{"other_item":"d5d0771b","description":"Granddaughter of","ranking":2,"is_relevant":true},{"other_item":"ce38b4dc","description":"Grand-niece of","ranking":3,"is_relevant":false}],"item_pictures":[{"picture":"","ranking":1}]},{"code":"d5d0771b","title":"Pietro Rinaldi","synopsis":"The wise grandfather who knew more than he let on and helps unlock Zeno's final secret.","ranking":3,"status":"ad3819b2","item_tags":[{"tag":"9ebd8391"}],"item_names":[{"code":"ac47de1c","name":"Grandpa","ranking":1},{"code":"d2bd3d5c","name":"Pietro","ranking":2}],"item_metadatas":[{"metadata_element":"5656e0b7.jpg","value":"~70"},{"metadata_element":"42bc76ed.jpg","value":"Mentor"}],"item_relationships":[{"other_item":"ce38b4dc","description":"Brother to","ranking":1,"is_relevant":true},{"other_item":"7ef69440","description":"Grandfather to","ranking":2,"is_relevant":true},{"other_item":"98a09da8","description":"Grandfather to","ranking":3,"is_relevant":true}],"item_pictures":[{"picture":"","ranking":1}]},{"code":"ce38b4dc","title":"Zeno Rinaldi","synopsis":"The vanished lighthouse keeper whose clues drive the story, and whose moral compass shaped the legacy.","ranking":4,"status":"ad3819b2","item_tags":[{"tag":"93f841a9"}],"item_names":[{"code":"d339fcec","name":"Zeno","ranking":1},{"code":"138be75d","name":"Rinaldi","ranking":2},{"code":"9036a044","name":"Z. R.","ranking":3}],"item_metadatas":[{"metadata_element":"42bc76ed.jpg","value":"Catalyst (off-screen)"},{"metadata_element":"1ea2a136.jpg","value":"Deceased (vanished decades earlier)"}],"item_relationships":[{"other_item":"d5d0771b","description":"Brother to","ranking":1,"is_relevant":true},{"other_item":"7ef69440","description":"Grandfather to","ranking":2,"is_relevant":true},{"other_item":"7ef69440","description":"Grand-uncle to","ranking":3,"is_relevant":false},{"other_item":"98a09da8","description":"Grand-uncle to","ranking":4,"is_relevant":false}]},{"code":"e2030757","title":"Arturo Marini","synopsis":"A former intelligence officer and Zeno's old colleague, now trying to protect the same truth.","ranking":5,"status":"ad3819b2","item_tags":[{"tag":"62647291"}],"item_names":[{"code":"7ef1879b","name":"Arturo","ranking":1},{"code":"b8469cd3","name":"Marini","ranking":2}],"item_metadatas":[{"metadata_element":"5656e0b7.jpg","value":"~60"},{"metadata_element":"42bc76ed.jpg","value":"Antagonist-turned-ally"}]}]},{"code":"33c592ab","title":"Locations","color":4294940672,"ranking":4,"tags":[{"code":"f1761e65","title":"Climatic","color":4280923894},{"code":"c0b2e8c3","title":"Haunted","color":4278193158},{"code":"312e6d3a","title":"Layered","color":4287458915},{"code":"d149f5cf","title":"Safe","color":4284922730},{"code":"65525483","title":"Threshold","color":4294953512},{"code":"22245c0a","title":"Unsafe","color":4294930499}],"items":[{"code":"c726509f","title":"Santa Marea","ranking":1,"status":"1","item_tags":[{"tag":"d149f5cf"}],"item_names":[{"code":"6730f0d1","name":"Santa Marea","ranking":1}],"item_notes":[{"text":"Add a short synopsis","ranking":1}],"item_pictures":[{"picture":"","ranking":1}]},{"code":"7de51c19","title":"The Lighthouse","synopsis":"Abandoned and crumbling, it hides Zeno's clues, secrets and final compartment.","ranking":2,"status":"ad3819b2","item_tags":[{"tag":"312e6d3a"},{"tag":"c0b2e8c3"}],"item_pictures":[{"picture":"","ranking":1}]},{"code":"51c51e68","title":"Cave of Voices","synopsis":"Tidal cave where coded carvings are hidden, accessible only at low tide.","ranking":3,"status":"ad3819b2","item_tags":[{"tag":"c0b2e8c3"},{"tag":"65525483"}],"item_names":[{"code":"27739ee8","name":"Cave of Voices","ranking":1},{"code":"d0b30496","name":"Grotta delle Voci","ranking":2}],"item_pictures":[{"picture":"","ranking":1}]},{"code":"6ce0de57","title":"The Boathouse","synopsis":"Dilapidated coastal shack concealing the cache of classified documents.","ranking":4,"status":"ad3819b2","item_tags":[{"tag":"22245c0a"}],"item_pictures":[{"picture":"","ranking":1}]},{"code":"f10f4783","title":"Cliffside Chapel","synopsis":"A neutral meeting point where Arturo reveals his intentions.","ranking":5,"status":"ad3819b2","item_tags":[{"tag":"f1761e65"}],"item_pictures":[{"picture":"","ranking":1}]}]},{"code":"f3f3ab2d","title":"Props","color":4284513675,"ranking":5,"items":[{"code":"42af6292","title":"Vespa","ranking":1,"status":"1","item_names":[{"code":"00978e8e","name":"Vespa","ranking":1}],"item_notes":[{"text":"Is it relevant?","ranking":1}],"item_pictures":[{"picture":"","ranking":1}]},{"code":"f7379308","title":"Elettra","ranking":2,"status":"1","item_names":[{"code":"ad120317","name":"Elettra","ranking":1}],"item_notes":[{"text":"Add a short description of the ship","ranking":1}],"item_pictures":[{"picture":"","ranking":1}]},{"code":"2f56a56c","title":"Zeno's Journal","synopsis":"Weathered notebook containing Zeno's codes, maps, and thoughts.","ranking":3,"status":"ad3819b2","item_pictures":[{"picture":"","ranking":1}]},{"code":"5da0f869","title":"Brass Fish Key","synopsis":"Unique key that fits a hidden lock in the lighthouse.","ranking":4,"status":"ad3819b2","item_pictures":[{"picture":"","ranking":1}]},{"code":"09372194","title":"Film Reel","synopsis":"Final evidence containing proof of a cover-up.","ranking":5,"status":"ad3819b2","item_pictures":[{"picture":"","ranking":1}]},{"code":"51ba8c45","title":"The Lantern","synopsis":"Old oil lantern found warm in the lighthouse; hints at recent presence.","ranking":6,"status":"ad3819b2","item_pictures":[{"picture":"","ranking":1}]}]}],"statuses":[{"code":"1","title":"To do","color":4292270041,"ranking":1},{"code":"10749586","title":"Draft","color":4294951175,"ranking":2},{"code":"ad3819b2","title":"Done","color":4283215696,"ranking":3}],"subplots":[{"code":"9e700349","title":"Uncovering Zeno's past","color":4289705003,"ranking":1},{"code":"7cea045a","title":"Arturo's evolving role","color":4280923894,"ranking":2},{"code":"f92f5d9c","title":"Pietro's eventual openness","color":4294948685,"ranking":3}],"scenes":[{"code":"fbfae51b","title":"A Boring Summer... or So He Thought","synopsis":"Tom Rinaldi arrives in Santa Marea, sulking and glued to his tablet, only to be greeted by his older cousin Irene, who’s excited to show him around the coastal town. The lighthouse looms in the distance.","text":"{\"blocks\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"￼ ￼ hated sand. It got between his toes, scratched up his tablet screen, and always seemed to find its way into his snacks. So when the train pulled into the tiny seaside station of ￼, he let out a long, theatrical sigh.\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":0,\"code\":\"2950d705\",\"value\":\"Tommaso\"},{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":2,\"code\":\"e90908a3\",\"value\":\"Rinaldi\"},{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":182,\"code\":\"6730f0d1\",\"value\":\"Santa Marea\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"«Seriously? No signal already?» he muttered, tapping his phone like it had betrayed him.\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"Outside the window, the town looked like something from a dusty postcard. Narrow cobbled streets. A few painted boats bobbing in a sleepy harbor. And, up on the hill, a crooked silhouette—the old lighthouse, long shut down and rumored to be haunted.\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"«￼!» came a cheerful voice. A girl with curly dark hair waved at him from the platform. She was wearing hiking boots, cargo shorts, and an enormous grin.\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":1,\"code\":\"85676f52\",\"value\":\"Tom\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"It was his cousin, ￼.\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":19,\"code\":\"d985eab4\",\"value\":\"Irene\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"«Your backpack weighs more than you do,» she said, grabbing it before he could complain. «Come on, ￼’s waiting with the ￼.»\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":99,\"code\":\"ac47de1c\",\"value\":\"Grandpa\"},{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":120,\"code\":\"00978e8e\",\"value\":\"Vespa\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"￼ squinted at the blazing sun and shuffled after her. He already missed the air conditioning.\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":0,\"code\":\"85676f52\",\"value\":\"Tom\"}]}]}","ranking":1,"status":"ad3819b2","scene_items":[{"code":"6acabda8"},{"code":"2c0fce79"},{"code":"7ef69440"},{"code":"98a09da8"},{"code":"d5d0771b"},{"code":"c726509f"},{"code":"42af6292"}]},{"code":"0885f709","title":"Grandpa's Stories","synopsis":"Over dinner, Grandpa Pietro tells the children about his brother Zeno, who vanished after a shipwreck decades earlier. He mentions that the lighthouse flickered to life the night Zeno disappeared.","text":"{\"blocks\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"￼ ￼'s house sat on the edge of a cliff, all crooked beams and the smell of salt and old wood. The kind of place where you half expected to find pirate treasure in the cellar—or a ghost in the pantry.\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":0,\"code\":\"ac47de1c\",\"value\":\"Grandpa\"},{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":2,\"code\":\"d2bd3d5c\",\"value\":\"Pietro\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"That evening, after a dinner of fried anchovies and roasted peppers, they sat on the terrace, the sea stretching out below them like a sheet of silver.\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"«Did you know,» ￼ ￼ began, puffing on his pipe, «that long ago, on nights like this, the lighthouse used to light up all on its own?»\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":16,\"code\":\"ac47de1c\",\"value\":\"Grandpa\"},{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":18,\"code\":\"d2bd3d5c\",\"value\":\"Pietro\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"￼ rolled his eyes. ￼ leaned forward.\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":0,\"code\":\"85676f52\",\"value\":\"Tom\"},{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":19,\"code\":\"d985eab4\",\"value\":\"Irene\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"«They said it was the ghost of ￼—my brother,» Pietro said, eyes narrowing. «He disappeared forty years ago. Vanished without a trace, just after the shipwreck of the ￼.»\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":31,\"code\":\"d339fcec\",\"value\":\"Zeno\"},{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":166,\"code\":\"ad120317\",\"value\":\"Elettra\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"«Shipwreck?» ￼ said, suddenly serious.\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":13,\"code\":\"d985eab4\",\"value\":\"Irene\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"«Cargo ship. Sank during a storm. Officially it was an accident. But ￼… ￼ believed it was sabotage. He was looking into it. Said there was a secret aboard. Something worth killing for.»\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":69,\"code\":\"d339fcec\",\"value\":\"Zeno\"},{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":72,\"code\":\"d339fcec\",\"value\":\"Zeno\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"￼ blinked. «So… did he find it?»\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":0,\"code\":\"85676f52\",\"value\":\"Tom\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"«No one knows,» ￼ said. «But the night he vanished, the lighthouse flickered to life. One last time.»\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":16,\"code\":\"ac47de1c\",\"value\":\"Grandpa\"}]}]}","ranking":2,"status":"ad3819b2","scene_subplots":[{"subplot":"9e700349","synopsis":"This early memory seeds the emotional core that pay off in the later scenes."}],"scene_items":[{"code":"ef69e892"},{"code":"6acabda8"},{"code":"7ef69440"},{"code":"98a09da8"},{"code":"d5d0771b"},{"code":"ce38b4dc"},{"code":"f7379308"}]},{"code":"e84c9d28","title":"The Flickering Light","synopsis":"Late at night, Tom sees a flickering light coming from the supposedly-abandoned lighthouse. He wakes Irene, and they decide to investigate.","text":"{\"blocks\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"￼ couldn’t sleep. Maybe it was the sound of waves, or the lingering scent of salt and oil on his pillow. Or maybe it was the story about ￼. He turned over and checked his tablet: battery 3%, no Wi-Fi. Useless.\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":0,\"code\":\"85676f52\",\"value\":\"Tom\"},{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":137,\"code\":\"d339fcec\",\"value\":\"Zeno\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"He got up and wandered to the window.\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"That’s when he saw it.\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"A faint pulse, like a blink of light, from the lighthouse tower.\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"He rubbed his eyes. The place had been out of service for decades. There was no electricity. No keeper. No reason for it to shine.\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"But there it was again.\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"Blink. Pause. Blink-blink. Long pause.\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"He wasn’t sure, but it almost looked like… a code.\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"He backed away from the window and tiptoed down the hall.\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"«￼,» he whispered, nudging her door open. «Wake up.»\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":1,\"code\":\"d985eab4\",\"value\":\"Irene\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"She groaned, buried under her blanket. «If you say there's Wi-Fi outside I swear—»\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"«The lighthouse,» ￼ said. «It’s flashing. I think someone’s in there.»\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":18,\"code\":\"85676f52\",\"value\":\"Tom\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"Irene was silent for a second.\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"Then she threw off the covers and grinned.\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"«Grab your shoes.»\"}]}","ranking":3,"status":"ad3819b2","scene_items":[{"code":"2c0fce79"},{"code":"49e8add7"},{"code":"7ef69440"},{"code":"98a09da8"},{"code":"7de51c19"}]},{"code":"d1c44f94","title":"Into The Lighthouse","synopsis":"Tom and Irene sneak into the lighthouse and find it recently disturbed. They discover a hidden trunk containing an old leather journal belonging to Zeno Rinaldi.","text":"{\"blocks\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"It took them twenty minutes to climb the hill. The path was half-eaten by weeds and thorns, and ￼ regretted not changing out of his flip-flops. The lighthouse loomed ahead, its white paint peeling like old scabs. The metal door was chained shut—but Irene was already kneeling beside it with a hairpin.\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":96,\"code\":\"85676f52\",\"value\":\"Tom\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"«Where did you learn to pick locks?» ￼ hissed.\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":37,\"code\":\"85676f52\",\"value\":\"Tom\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"«Internet,» she said. Click.\",\"spans\":[{\"type\":\"italic\",\"start\":22,\"end\":28}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"Inside, the air was thick with dust and the smell of rust. Their flashlight beams bounced off the curved walls. The spiral staircase groaned as they climbed, each step echoing louder than the last.\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"When they reached the top, ￼ felt his heart jump.\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":27,\"code\":\"85676f52\",\"value\":\"Tom\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"The lens was cracked, the control panel smashed—but lying next to it was a lantern. Not an electric one—a real oil lantern. Still warm.\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"«Someone’s been here,» ￼ whispered.\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":23,\"code\":\"85676f52\",\"value\":\"Tom\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"«And not long ago.»\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"Then ￼ spotted the trunk in the corner, hidden under a stained tarp. She tugged it open. Inside were moldy books, a tangle of ropes, and something wrapped in cloth.\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":5,\"code\":\"d985eab4\",\"value\":\"Irene\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"She unwrapped it slowly.\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"A journal. The leather cover was worn, but the initials on it were still clear: ￼\",\"spans\":[{\"type\":\"bold\",\"start\":80,\"end\":81}],\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":80,\"code\":\"9036a044\",\"value\":\"Z. R.\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"«￼ ￼,» she murmured. «It’s his.»\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":1,\"code\":\"d339fcec\",\"value\":\"Zeno\"},{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":3,\"code\":\"e90908a3\",\"value\":\"Rinaldi\"}]}]}","ranking":4,"status":"ad3819b2","scene_items":[{"code":"ef69e892"},{"code":"2c0fce79"},{"code":"12aaee20"},{"code":"7ef69440"},{"code":"98a09da8"},{"code":"7de51c19"},{"code":"2f56a56c"},{"code":"51ba8c45"}]},{"code":"eae8f868","title":"The Coded Message","synopsis":"Inside the journal, they find sea charts, notes, and a cryptic line—“The sea hides what the stars reveal”—along with a coded message. They match it with a star chart and identify a coastal cave as the next location.","text":"{\"blocks\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"Back in the attic at ￼’s house, the two cousins huddled around the journal. Its pages were filled with messy writing, sketches of sea charts, tide tables—and strange, looping symbols that weren’t letters at all.\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":21,\"code\":\"ac47de1c\",\"value\":\"Grandpa\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"«Most of this is normal,» ￼ said, flipping pages. «Notes about storms, currents, boat names. But then… this.»\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":26,\"code\":\"d985eab4\",\"value\":\"Irene\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"She pointed at one page. It showed the phrase:\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"“The sea hides what the stars reveal.”\",\"spans\":[{\"type\":\"bold\",\"start\":0,\"end\":38}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"Underneath was a line of symbols: stars, waves, spirals, dots. ￼ took a picture with his phone.\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":63,\"code\":\"85676f52\",\"value\":\"Tom\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"«I don’t get it,» he said. «Why write in code?»\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"«Because someone didn’t want this found,» ￼ said. «Remember what ￼ said? ￼ believed there was a secret on that ship. What if he discovered something… and hid it?»\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":42,\"code\":\"d985eab4\",\"value\":\"Irene\"},{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":65,\"code\":\"ac47de1c\",\"value\":\"Grandpa\"},{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":73,\"code\":\"d339fcec\",\"value\":\"Zeno\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"They spread out the rest of the items from the trunk. At the very bottom, wedged under the false bottom, ￼ found a folded piece of paper—brittle with age.\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":105,\"code\":\"d985eab4\",\"value\":\"Irene\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"It was a star chart.\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"￼’s eyes lit up. «Wait… wait, the line in the journal—“The sea hides what the stars reveal.” What if it’s literal?»\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":0,\"code\":\"85676f52\",\"value\":\"Tom\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"They overlay the coded symbols onto the star chart and lined them up with the constellations.\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"Where the symbols matched the stars, one location stood out—marked by a little “X” just off the coast, beside the cliffs known as ￼.\",\"spans\":[{\"type\":\"bold\",\"start\":130,\"end\":131}],\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":130,\"code\":\"d0b30496\",\"value\":\"Grotta delle Voci\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"«The ￼,» ￼ whispered. «Only visible at low tide.»\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":9,\"code\":\"d985eab4\",\"value\":\"Irene\"},{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":5,\"code\":\"27739ee8\",\"value\":\"Cave of Voices\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"«And that’s in…» ￼ checked the tide schedule in the journal. «Tomorrow morning.»\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":17,\"code\":\"85676f52\",\"value\":\"Tom\"}]}]}","ranking":5,"status":"ad3819b2","scene_items":[{"code":"ef69e892"},{"code":"6acabda8"},{"code":"7ef69440"},{"code":"98a09da8"},{"code":"ce38b4dc"},{"code":"2f56a56c"},{"code":"5da0f869"}]},{"code":"578039d2","title":"Beneath the Floorboards","synopsis":"Later, Tom returns alone and finds a compartment beneath the lighthouse floorboards. Inside, he finds a brass fish-shaped key and a waterproof map marked with tidal symbols and a phrase hinting at hidden treasure.","text":"{\"blocks\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"￼ couldn’t sleep. Again.\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":0,\"code\":\"85676f52\",\"value\":\"Tom\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"This time, it wasn’t nerves—it was excitement. He was onto something. No games, no screens, no made-up stories. This was real.\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"He got up, turned on the desk lamp, and flipped through the journal one more time. There was something bothering him. On one of the final pages, a sketch of the lighthouse floor. An arrow pointing to one board. A tiny note in the corner:\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"“First step. Use the lantern.”\",\"spans\":[{\"type\":\"bold\",\"start\":0,\"end\":30}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"He crept downstairs to the garage, grabbed the lantern they’d found, and returned to the lighthouse alone. ￼ would be mad, but he couldn’t wait.\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":107,\"code\":\"d985eab4\",\"value\":\"Irene\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"In the tower, he lit the lantern and held it near the floor.\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"One board was a different color. Slightly warped.\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"He pried it up with the flat end of the lantern’s handle. Underneath, hidden in the dark:\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"A small compartment.\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"Inside: a brass key, shaped like a fish, and a map drawn on waterproof paper. It had tide marks, cave symbols—and a phrase written in the corner:\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"“What was lost at sea waits for the brave.”\",\"spans\":[{\"type\":\"bold\",\"start\":0,\"end\":43}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"￼ pocketed the key and the map.\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":0,\"code\":\"85676f52\",\"value\":\"Tom\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"Tomorrow, they'd go to the cave.\"}]}","ranking":6,"status":"ad3819b2","scene_items":[{"code":"2c0fce79"},{"code":"7ef69440"},{"code":"ce38b4dc"},{"code":"5da0f869"}]},{"code":"15257021","title":"Tide and Time","synopsis":"The next morning, Tom and Irene head out to explore the cave at low tide, following the symbols in the journal.","text":"{\"blocks\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"The next morning, just after dawn, ￼ met ￼ outside ￼’s gate. She had a backpack, a flashlight, and a coil of rope over one shoulder.\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":35,\"code\":\"d985eab4\",\"value\":\"Irene\"},{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":41,\"code\":\"85676f52\",\"value\":\"Tom\"},{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":51,\"code\":\"ac47de1c\",\"value\":\"Grandpa\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"«You went back without me,» she said flatly.\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"￼ held up the brass key like a trophy. «But look what I found!»\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":0,\"code\":\"85676f52\",\"value\":\"Tom\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"￼ raised an eyebrow. «You’re lucky I didn’t lock you in the chicken coop.»\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":0,\"code\":\"d985eab4\",\"value\":\"Irene\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"They followed the map toward the cliffs. The tide was low, the rocks slick with seawater and seaweed. Gulls wheeled overhead, crying like something out of an old pirate movie.\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"«There,» ￼ said, pointing.\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":9,\"code\":\"85676f52\",\"value\":\"Tom\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"Hidden behind a cluster of jagged rocks was the narrow mouth of a sea cave. Barely a meter high. ￼ clicked on her flashlight.\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":97,\"code\":\"d985eab4\",\"value\":\"Irene\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"«No signal,» ￼ muttered, checking his phone for the hundredth time.\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":13,\"code\":\"85676f52\",\"value\":\"Tom\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"«You think the treasure has Wi-Fi?»\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"They ducked inside.\"}]}","ranking":7,"status":"10749586","scene_items":[{"code":"2c0fce79"},{"code":"7ef69440"},{"code":"98a09da8"},{"code":"51c51e68"}]},{"code":"e669a68a","title":"The Cave of Voices","synopsis":"Inside the sea cave, they discover the same coded symbols carved into the walls. They’re interrupted by a mysterious man in a raincoat who seems to be following their trail.","text":"{\"blocks\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"The cave twisted and narrowed, the floor uneven and damp. Water dripped from the ceiling in slow, rhythmic taps. The deeper they went, the cooler the air became.\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"￼’s flashlight caught something on the wall—markings.\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":0,\"code\":\"85676f52\",\"value\":\"Tom\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"Stars, waves, and spirals. The same code from the journal.\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"￼ brushed away some moss. «It’s the same sequence,» she whispered.\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":0,\"code\":\"d985eab4\",\"value\":\"Irene\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"Just ahead, the passage widened into a chamber with a high ceiling. Echoes bounced strangely around them—like whispers.\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"«That’s why they call it the ￼,» ￼ said. «It’s just echoes.»\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":29,\"code\":\"27739ee8\",\"value\":\"Cave of Voices\"},{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":33,\"code\":\"85676f52\",\"value\":\"Tom\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"«Not just echoes,» said a voice.\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"The flashlight beam swung wildly. A figure stood at the entrance to the chamber—tall, in a dark raincoat and wide-brimmed hat. He wore thick boots and gloves, and his face was hidden in shadow.\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"￼ gasped. ￼’s heart kicked in his chest.\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":0,\"code\":\"d985eab4\",\"value\":\"Irene\"},{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":10,\"code\":\"85676f52\",\"value\":\"Tom\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"The man stepped forward.\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"«You shouldn’t be here.»\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"They turned and ran.\"}]}","ranking":8,"status":"10749586","scene_items":[{"code":"ef69e892"},{"code":"2c0fce79"},{"code":"7ef69440"},{"code":"98a09da8"},{"code":"e2030757"},{"code":"51c51e68"}]},{"code":"fd1e7a6a","title":"The Clue He Dropped","synopsis":"The cousins escape and find a photo and a set of coordinates dropped by the stranger, along with a cryptic note suggesting others are also hunting for Zeno’s secret.","text":"{\"blocks\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"The cave tunnel twisted behind them. ￼ slipped once, scraping his palm, but ￼ hauled him up. Behind them, the man’s footsteps echoed, but he wasn’t running—just walking steadily.\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":37,\"code\":\"85676f52\",\"value\":\"Tom\"},{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":76,\"code\":\"d985eab4\",\"value\":\"Irene\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"By the time they burst out into daylight, the tide was already creeping back in.\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"«He was following us,» ￼ panted. «Why wasn’t he faster?»\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":23,\"code\":\"85676f52\",\"value\":\"Tom\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"￼ didn’t answer. She was staring at something in the sand.\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":0,\"code\":\"d985eab4\",\"value\":\"Irene\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"A folded paper. It must’ve fallen from the man’s pocket.\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"She snatched it up. It was damp, but still readable—an old photograph of the lighthouse, and a set of handwritten coordinates. Below that, in sharp black ink: “￼’s secret. Find it before they do.”\",\"spans\":[{\"type\":\"bold\",\"start\":159,\"end\":196}],\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":160,\"code\":\"138be75d\",\"value\":\"Rinaldi\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"«Before who does?» ￼ asked.\",\"spans\":[{\"type\":\"italic\",\"start\":8,\"end\":11}],\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":19,\"code\":\"85676f52\",\"value\":\"Tom\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"￼ folded the paper, eyes scanning the horizon. «We need to figure that out. Fast.»\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":0,\"code\":\"d985eab4\",\"value\":\"Irene\"}]}]}","ranking":9,"status":"10749586","scene_subplots":[{"subplot":"7cea045a","synopsis":"Shifts him from mysterious threat to ambiguous ally."}],"scene_items":[{"code":"ef69e892"},{"code":"7ef69440"},{"code":"98a09da8"},{"code":"e2030757"}]},{"code":"377a3aa8","title":"The Man in the Raincoat","synopsis":"Back at home, they realize the symbol in the photo matches a carving on the lighthouse wall—possibly a hidden keyhole. The coordinates lead them to an abandoned military boathouse.","text":"{\"blocks\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"They didn’t speak much on the walk back. ￼ clutched the paper they’d found. ￼ kept glancing over his shoulder, half-expecting the man in the raincoat to appear on the road behind them.\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":76,\"code\":\"85676f52\",\"value\":\"Tom\"},{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":41,\"code\":\"d985eab4\",\"value\":\"Irene\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"Back at the house, ￼ ￼ was nowhere to be seen. Probably out at the market. The cousins slipped into the attic and spread out the photo and coordinates on the floor between them.\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":19,\"code\":\"ac47de1c\",\"value\":\"Grandpa\"},{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":21,\"code\":\"d2bd3d5c\",\"value\":\"Pietro\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"«It’s definitely the lighthouse,» ￼ said, tapping the photo. «But this... this symbol isn’t anywhere on the building.»\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":34,\"code\":\"85676f52\",\"value\":\"Tom\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"In the corner of the photo, almost hidden in shadow, was a carved shape in the stone wall—something like a fish wrapped around a star.\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"«It looks familiar,» ￼ muttered. She pulled the brass key from ￼'s backpack and held it up next to the image.\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":21,\"code\":\"d985eab4\",\"value\":\"Irene\"},{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":63,\"code\":\"85676f52\",\"value\":\"Tom\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"Perfect match.\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"«It’s a keyhole marker,» she said. «That symbol—it’s where the key fits.»\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"￼ blinked. «There’s a hidden lock… in the wall of the lighthouse?»\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":0,\"code\":\"85676f52\",\"value\":\"Tom\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"«Looks like it.»\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"They spent the next hour checking the coordinates. With the help of ￼’s old sea atlas, they pinpointed the location: a boathouse down the coast, once part of the military outpost during the war.\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":68,\"code\":\"ac47de1c\",\"value\":\"Grandpa\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"«￼’s trail didn’t stop at the lighthouse,» ￼ whispered. «He was hiding something… moving it.»\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":1,\"code\":\"d339fcec\",\"value\":\"Zeno\"},{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":43,\"code\":\"d985eab4\",\"value\":\"Irene\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"«And that man,» ￼ added. «He’s following the same trail.»\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":16,\"code\":\"85676f52\",\"value\":\"Tom\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"«But he’s missing something.» ￼ held up the key. «This.»\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":30,\"code\":\"d985eab4\",\"value\":\"Irene\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"A gust of wind rattled the attic window. ￼ shivered, but it wasn’t from the cold.\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":41,\"code\":\"85676f52\",\"value\":\"Tom\"}]}]}","ranking":10,"status":"ad3819b2","scene_items":[{"code":"ef69e892"},{"code":"6acabda8"},{"code":"7ef69440"},{"code":"98a09da8"},{"code":"ce38b4dc"},{"code":"e2030757"},{"code":"7de51c19"},{"code":"5da0f869"}]},{"code":"572e7678","title":"The Boathouse","synopsis":"In the hidden chamber of the boathouse, they find crates of classified wartime documents, charts, and letters that Zeno had hidden decades ago. It's not treasure—it’s government secrets.","text":"{\"blocks\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"The boathouse sat crookedly on the edge of a collapsed pier, half-eaten by salt and time. Most locals avoided it—it was rumored to be haunted, like everything else in ￼.\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":167,\"code\":\"6730f0d1\",\"value\":\"Santa Marea\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"￼ and ￼ waited until sunset to go. Less chance of being seen.\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":0,\"code\":\"85676f52\",\"value\":\"Tom\"},{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":6,\"code\":\"d985eab4\",\"value\":\"Irene\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"Inside, the boathouse smelled of fish oil and old nets. A rusty rowboat hung upside-down from the rafters. Waves lapped quietly beneath the floorboards.\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"They searched in silence, feeling the weight of the air. ￼ tapped on the walls with a rock, listening for hollows. ￼ checked under broken floorboards, half-hoping to find bones, half-hoping not to.\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":57,\"code\":\"d985eab4\",\"value\":\"Irene\"},{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":115,\"code\":\"85676f52\",\"value\":\"Tom\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"Then ￼ froze.\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":5,\"code\":\"d985eab4\",\"value\":\"Irene\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"«Here,» she whispered.\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"Behind a stack of salt-crusted crates was a narrow panel of wood that didn’t match the rest. She pressed her ear against it, then shoved. It creaked, then gave way.\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"Behind it: a small, dark chamber.\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"They ducked inside.\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"The chamber was lined with concrete, no windows, no furniture. Just a single crate in the center, wrapped in oiled canvas. ￼ pulled out her pocketknife and sliced the rope.\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":123,\"code\":\"d985eab4\",\"value\":\"Irene\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"Inside: folders. Dozens of them. Stamped with old government seals. Maps. Letters. Blueprints. All yellowed with age.\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"￼ picked up one and read aloud.\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":0,\"code\":\"85676f52\",\"value\":\"Tom\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"“Operation Sirena. August 1945. Submarine routes off the Italian coast... encrypted logs, interception orders...”\",\"spans\":[{\"type\":\"italic\",\"start\":0,\"end\":113}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"He looked up. «This isn’t treasure.»\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"«No,» ￼ said. «It’s information. Secrets.»\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":6,\"code\":\"d985eab4\",\"value\":\"Irene\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"￼ hadn’t been chasing gold.\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":0,\"code\":\"d339fcec\",\"value\":\"Zeno\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"He had been protecting something far more dangerous.\"}]}","ranking":11,"status":"ad3819b2","scene_items":[{"code":"ef69e892"},{"code":"624e4be1"},{"code":"7ef69440"},{"code":"98a09da8"},{"code":"ce38b4dc"},{"code":"6ce0de57"}]},{"code":"0db18aac","title":"Zeno's Final Message","synopsis":"A letter from Zeno warns that knowledge can be dangerous and must be protected. He trusted only family to carry on his work. Meanwhile, the man in the raincoat is spotted watching from the cliffs.","text":"{\"blocks\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"In the bottom of the crate was a sealed envelope, addressed in elegant handwriting:\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"To ￼. For when the truth is safer than the silence.\",\"spans\":[{\"type\":\"bold\",\"start\":0,\"end\":51}],\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":3,\"code\":\"d2bd3d5c\",\"value\":\"Pietro\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"￼ opened it with trembling hands. Inside was a letter and a small black-and-white photo of two boys sitting on the lighthouse steps—￼ and ￼, barely ten years old.\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":0,\"code\":\"d985eab4\",\"value\":\"Irene\"},{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":132,\"code\":\"d2bd3d5c\",\"value\":\"Pietro\"},{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":138,\"code\":\"d339fcec\",\"value\":\"Zeno\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"The letter explained everything.\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"￼ had discovered that during the war, the ￼ had secretly transported military documents disguised as civilian cargo. After the shipwreck, he’d traced pieces of the cargo to the lighthouse, and then here. But someone else had caught wind of it too—someone who didn’t want those files to see the light of day.\",\"spans\":[{\"type\":\"italic\",\"start\":42,\"end\":43}],\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":0,\"code\":\"d339fcec\",\"value\":\"Zeno\"},{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":42,\"code\":\"ad120317\",\"value\":\"Elettra\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"«I hid them,» Zeno wrote. «Because knowledge is a kind of treasure, and it must not fall into the wrong hands.»\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"At the bottom of the letter was a final message:\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"If you're reading this, someone has followed you. Don’t trust anyone—except blood.\",\"spans\":[{\"type\":\"bold\",\"start\":0,\"end\":82}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"￼ looked at ￼. «The man in the cave... He must’ve been looking for this.»\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":0,\"code\":\"85676f52\",\"value\":\"Tom\"},{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":12,\"code\":\"d985eab4\",\"value\":\"Irene\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"￼ nodded. «And now he knows we’re ahead of him.»\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":0,\"code\":\"d985eab4\",\"value\":\"Irene\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"They stared at the files, at ￼’s warnings, and then at each other.\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":29,\"code\":\"d339fcec\",\"value\":\"Zeno\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"«We have to tell ￼,» ￼ said.\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":17,\"code\":\"ac47de1c\",\"value\":\"Grandpa\"},{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":21,\"code\":\"d985eab4\",\"value\":\"Irene\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"«But not yet,» ￼ said quietly.\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":15,\"code\":\"85676f52\",\"value\":\"Tom\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"She tilted her head. «Why not?»\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"«Because he might not believe us. Not without proof. We need to finish what ￼ started.»\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":76,\"code\":\"d339fcec\",\"value\":\"Zeno\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"Outside, the wind had picked up. And in the distance, down the coastal path, a figure stood just watching.\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"The man in the raincoat.\"}]}","ranking":12,"status":"ad3819b2","scene_subplots":[{"subplot":"9e700349","synopsis":"The closing of his mystery has impact on Tom and Irene'a motivations, and shapes their view of legacy."}],"scene_items":[{"code":"ef69e892"},{"code":"6acabda8"},{"code":"7ef69440"},{"code":"98a09da8"},{"code":"ce38b4dc"}]},{"code":"32c06b45","title":"The Final Confrontation","synopsis":"The man confronts them at the lighthouse, revealing he was once Zeno’s colleague and ally. He warns them others are searching too—and that time is running out.","text":"{\"blocks\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"They didn’t go back to ￼’s house. Not yet.\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":23,\"code\":\"ac47de1c\",\"value\":\"Grandpa\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"Instead, ￼ and ￼ took the crate of documents and hid it in the back of the lighthouse, beneath the spiral stairs, in a space ￼ himself had once used. Then they waited.\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":9,\"code\":\"d985eab4\",\"value\":\"Irene\"},{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":15,\"code\":\"85676f52\",\"value\":\"Tom\"},{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":125,\"code\":\"d339fcec\",\"value\":\"Zeno\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"And the man came.\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"Just after dusk, footsteps crunched on gravel outside. A knock on the metal door echoed through the tower.\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"They didn’t answer.\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"A second knock. Firmer.\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"Then silence.\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"￼ peeked through a crack in the upper wall. The man was still wearing the raincoat, even in the summer heat. He looked older now, close up. His hair was grey, his face lined. And something in his eyes—restless, sharp, angry—reminded ￼ of a stray dog cornered too many times.\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":0,\"code\":\"85676f52\",\"value\":\"Tom\"},{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":233,\"code\":\"85676f52\",\"value\":\"Tom\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"Then, to their surprise, the man called out.\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"«I don’t want to hurt anyone.»\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"His voice was hoarse, but not unkind.\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"«I worked with ￼ ￼. A long time ago. We weren’t friends. But we were... aligned.»\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":15,\"code\":\"d339fcec\",\"value\":\"Zeno\"},{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":17,\"code\":\"138be75d\",\"value\":\"Rinaldi\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"￼ and ￼ looked at each other.\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":0,\"code\":\"85676f52\",\"value\":\"Tom\"},{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":6,\"code\":\"d985eab4\",\"value\":\"Irene\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"«I came back to finish what he started,» the man continued. «But I’m not the only one looking anymore. There are others. And they won’t be careful like me.»\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"He stepped back from the door, slowly.\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"«When you’re ready, bring the files to the cliff chapel. Tomorrow. Noon.»\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"He turned and walked away.\"}]}","ranking":13,"status":"ad3819b2","scene_items":[{"code":"ef69e892"},{"code":"2c0fce79"},{"code":"7ef69440"},{"code":"98a09da8"},{"code":"e2030757"},{"code":"7de51c19"}]},{"code":"086583ad","title":"Pietro's Secret","synopsis":"The cousins confide in Grandpa Pietro, who reveals that he suspected Zeno was hiding something important. He helps them retrieve a final reel of film hidden in the lighthouse, containing damning evidence.","text":"{\"blocks\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"That night, they told ￼ everything.\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":22,\"code\":\"ac47de1c\",\"value\":\"Grandpa\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"They expected disbelief. But ￼ ￼ said nothing for a long time. Then he opened an old drawer and took out a key.\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":29,\"code\":\"ac47de1c\",\"value\":\"Grandpa\"},{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":31,\"code\":\"d2bd3d5c\",\"value\":\"Pietro\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"«I knew ￼ had found something,» he said quietly. «But he never told me what. He just said… if anything happened to him, to protect the lighthouse. And wait.»\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":8,\"code\":\"d339fcec\",\"value\":\"Zeno\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"«Wait for what?» Irene asked.\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"«For someone brave enough to go further than we did,» ￼ said. He handed ￼ the key. «There’s a panel in the lamp room. You’ve seen the fake wall?»\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":54,\"code\":\"d2bd3d5c\",\"value\":\"Pietro\"},{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":72,\"code\":\"85676f52\",\"value\":\"Tom\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"￼ nodded.\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":0,\"code\":\"85676f52\",\"value\":\"Tom\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"«￼ built it. To hide the last piece.»\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":1,\"code\":\"d339fcec\",\"value\":\"Zeno\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"The next morning, just before sunrise, ￼ and ￼ returned to the tower and opened the hidden panel. Inside was a steel case, locked but still dry. The key fit perfectly.\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":39,\"code\":\"85676f52\",\"value\":\"Tom\"},{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":45,\"code\":\"d985eab4\",\"value\":\"Irene\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"Inside: a single reel of film.\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"With it: a letter.\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"To whomever continues this search:\",\"spans\":[{\"type\":\"bold\",\"start\":0,\"end\":34},{\"type\":\"italic\",\"start\":34,\"end\":34}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"What you hold is evidence of a conspiracy that spans oceans and decades. It is not gold. It is not glory. It is truth—and truth is always dangerous.\",\"spans\":[{\"type\":\"italic\",\"start\":0,\"end\":148},{\"type\":\"bold\",\"start\":0,\"end\":0}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"—Zeno Rinaldi\",\"spans\":[{\"type\":\"italic\",\"start\":0,\"end\":0}]}]}","ranking":14,"status":"ad3819b2","scene_subplots":[{"subplot":"f92f5d9c","synopsis":"Pietro's withholding and final support parallels the theme of intergenerational trust."}],"scene_items":[{"code":"ef69e892"},{"code":"6acabda8"},{"code":"f9cf101c"},{"code":"7ef69440"},{"code":"98a09da8"},{"code":"d5d0771b"},{"code":"ce38b4dc"},{"code":"7de51c19"},{"code":"5da0f869"},{"code":"09372194"}]},{"code":"867ced3c","title":"The Light and the Legacy","synopsis":"They turn over the files and film to a trusted journalist. Zeno’s name is cleared, the conspiracy is exposed, and the lighthouse is restored as a symbol of truth. The light shines again, this time not just as a beacon for sailors—but for history.","text":"{\"blocks\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"At noon, they met the man on the cliff behind the chapel.\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"He took off his raincoat. Underneath, he wore an old naval uniform, worn thin but neatly kept. On his chest, the insignia of a coastal intelligence officer.\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"«My name’s ￼ ￼,» he said. «I was on the ￼ once. I followed orders, even the bad ones. ￼ tried to expose what we were carrying. I told him to stay out of it.»\",\"spans\":[{\"type\":\"italic\",\"start\":40,\"end\":41}],\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":11,\"code\":\"7ef1879b\",\"value\":\"Arturo\"},{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":13,\"code\":\"b8469cd3\",\"value\":\"Marini\"},{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":40,\"code\":\"ad120317\",\"value\":\"Elettra\"},{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":86,\"code\":\"d339fcec\",\"value\":\"Zeno\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"￼ handed him the reel of film. «So what now?»\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":0,\"code\":\"85676f52\",\"value\":\"Tom\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"￼ looked at the case. «Now we finish what he started.»\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":0,\"code\":\"7ef1879b\",\"value\":\"Arturo\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"Together, they brought the documents to a journalist in the nearest city. Within days, the story began to unfold—how encrypted wartime files were buried and forgotten, how a young lighthouse keeper tried to protect them, and vanished doing so.\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"￼’s name was cleared.\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":0,\"code\":\"d339fcec\",\"value\":\"Zeno\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"His story finally told.\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"And the lighthouse?\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"That night, it shone again.\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"Not automatically, not magically—but properly, restored and gleaming, its beam sweeping across the dark sea like a sentinel awakened.\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"￼ ￼ stood beside ￼ and ￼, arm around each of their shoulders.\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":0,\"code\":\"ac47de1c\",\"value\":\"Grandpa\"},{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":2,\"code\":\"d2bd3d5c\",\"value\":\"Pietro\"},{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":17,\"code\":\"85676f52\",\"value\":\"Tom\"},{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":23,\"code\":\"d985eab4\",\"value\":\"Irene\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"«I knew there was something special about you two,» he said.\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"￼ looked up at the tower, the glass catching the moonlight. «It’s not just a lighthouse anymore, is it?»\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":0,\"code\":\"85676f52\",\"value\":\"Tom\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"«No,» ￼ said. «It’s a monument.»\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":6,\"code\":\"d985eab4\",\"value\":\"Irene\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"«To truth,» said ￼.\",\"embeds\":[{\"type\":\"mention\",\"position\":17,\"code\":\"ac47de1c\",\"value\":\"Grandpa\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"«To Zeno,» said Tom.\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text\":\"And the light turned once more.\"}]}","ranking":15,"status":"ad3819b2","scene_items":[{"code":"ef69e892"},{"code":"6acabda8"},{"code":"7ef69440"},{"code":"98a09da8"},{"code":"d5d0771b"},{"code":"ce38b4dc"},{"code":"e2030757"},{"code":"f10f4783"},{"code":"2f56a56c"},{"code":"09372194"},{"code":"51ba8c45"}]}],"sections":[{"code":"3683e8ff","title":"Chapter 1: Arrival in Santa Marea","synopsis":"Tom arrives in Santa Marea and hears Grandpa’s tale about the vanished Zeno and a mysterious lighthouse light. That night, Tom sees the light for himself—and wakes Irene to investigate.","ranking":1,"section_scenes":[{"code":"fbfae51b","ranking":1},{"code":"0885f709","ranking":2},{"code":"e84c9d28","ranking":3}]},{"code":"451f5e88","title":"Chapter 2: The Journal","synopsis":"Inside the lighthouse, they find Zeno’s journal, a coded message, and a star chart. Tom later uncovers a hidden key and map beneath the floor, pointing to a cave revealed at low tide.","ranking":2,"section_scenes":[{"code":"d1c44f94","ranking":1},{"code":"eae8f868","ranking":2},{"code":"578039d2","ranking":3}]},{"code":"3c117173","title":"Chapter 3: The First Key","synopsis":"In the sea cave, they discover more clues—but are startled by a mysterious man in a raincoat. After escaping, they find a dropped photo and coordinates, suggesting someone else is hunting the same secret.","ranking":3,"section_scenes":[{"code":"15257021","ranking":1},{"code":"e669a68a","ranking":2},{"code":"fd1e7a6a","ranking":3}]},{"code":"fe8ff2ac","title":"Chapter 4: Shadows and Secrets","synopsis":"Following the coordinates, Tom and Irene uncover a hidden room with wartime documents Zeno had protected. A final letter warns them of danger—and the stranger appears again, watching from afar.","ranking":4,"section_scenes":[{"code":"377a3aa8","ranking":1},{"code":"572e7678","ranking":2},{"code":"0db18aac","ranking":3}]},{"code":"33b13d39","title":"Chapter 5: The Truth Behind the Light","synopsis":"The stranger reveals he was Zeno’s ally and warns of others seeking the documents. With Grandpa’s help, the cousins retrieve the final evidence and expose the truth. The lighthouse shines again in Zeno’s honor.","ranking":5,"section_scenes":[{"code":"32c06b45","ranking":1},{"code":"086583ad","ranking":2},{"code":"867ced3c","ranking":3}]}]}]}